The lack of snow in mountain bothers hoteliers
The runways deserted do not pose a problem that operators of remonte-pentes.
The lack of snow discourages people to book their stays in skiing in hotels and pensions.
As a result, it is still possible to find free rooms for all dates in winter, including Christmas and New Year.
We have a lot of visits on our site.
Internet users roam the offers, asking prices but dare not commit to set aside for the moment.
And if they call, they ask immediately if there will be snow or mud at Christmas, "said Martin Jandura, operator of the information portal Spindl.Info.
If you want to spend New Year's Eve of his dreams to Špindlerův Mlýn, better not too reluctant to book.
If the priority is given to the economies and that the quality of accommodation only then, then we can try to wait a few more days.
Hoteliers of Špindler propose for the moment that stays a week for the New Year.
I think they will try one more time of the place, but they also cèderont and accept shorter periods.
And then the number of rooms free will rapidly diminish, "said Jandura.
The tourism agency Ingtours of Vrchlabí also proposes yet beds of free for all periods of winter.
The week of Christmas we most interested at the moment, it is not completely sold.
There are still free, say, half of the rooms in our offer.
That is why we have already prepared a few last-minute Christmas stays cheaper, "said the director of Ingtours Petr Schiefert.
The agency Vrchlabí tourism may also propose the New Year to Krkonoše, but there are fewer empty seats.
The first fourteen days of February go well, the remaining winter trips sell moderately.
This year, the interest for stays of winter has been negatively influenced by the fact that there is still no snow to Krkonoše.
People expect that it will start to fall.
Nobody wants to spend the winter in the mountain without snow.
If the runways overlap during the week, Christmas also will be complete, "think Schiefert.
Conversely, the occupation of the hotel Horizont Pec pod Sněžkou is slightly higher than last year.
It was an improvement of about five percent.
We still have few places for the New Year as for Christmas.
There is a great interest during the holidays in January of Polish and February sells well too, "advises Karel Rada, Director of the best hotel in Pec.
The hotel Omnia near the central park of Jánské Lázně is also full of eighty percent during the period of the New Year.
On the contrary, half of the beds are empty at Christmas in the most recent hotel Jánské Lázně.
This year, we were pleasantly surprised by the month of January, where we have already sixty percent of occupation at the moment.
February is a little more low at the moment, but as soon as the snow will fall, the interest for stays in the Krkonoše builds certainly still indicated the director of the hotel Omnia, Erik Sporysch.
The hotel of Krkonoše should not expect more snow.
On Thursday it will more fees and if there is precipitation, they should be neigeuses mountain.
But by the time should be warm, inform Jiří Jakubský of Hradec station of the Czech Hydrometeorological Institute.
United States: repetition is the mother of wisdom
It becomes even comique, the diligence with which Barack Obama, president of the reputation of wise, reproduced the strategy of his predecessor on the Afghan question, that he considered himself as simple.
When he eventually leave sweat its doctrine so eagerly awaited, it turned out that he had recopied in carbon paper since the Iraq scenario of Bush of three years ago.
Not content to use in the text itself several times the expression "as in Iraq," he has not hesitated, moreover, to use the title of the speech by Bush in January 2007 as the title of his own speech: "A new road ahead"
At the same time, he has personally criticized the idea of Bush to send new reinforcements in Iraq consumed by the civil war as "irresponsible and a disastrous decision in its consequences."
The following month, however, have shown that the strategy of Bush, who came to the recommendations of commanders of campaigns, was the only possible and likely success to the point that the newspapers currently do not speak at all of Iraq.
This has not enhanced the reputation of Bush, however, objectively speaking, it has left his successor a final situation much more favourable than we might hope.
Barack Obama hope that in Afghanistan, the miracle will happen again
It is again the commanders of campaigns that have requested an increase in the military contingent, including the commander of the operation in Afghanistan, General Stanley McCristal, which has even severely criticized the reluctance of the White House despite the habits of subordination.
He asked 40,000 men in order to make the situation more favourable.
The president has hesitated for three months but in the absence of a better option, at least he had defrauded the general of 10,000 soldiers.
He has managed to root out the promise of 5 000 extra on the part of Europe, even if it were on 10 000.
This brings the most problems throughout the strategy of Obama appears to be its intention to withdraw the armies of Afghanistan by 18 months and complete the whole process within three years. The entire doctrine of Obama raises more questions than it provides answers.
Many doubt the fact that an increase of half will bring the same fruit that progress in Iraq.
Despite the fratricidal wars in recent years, Iraqi society is relatively well organized and its leaders to honour the agreements.
The Afghan situation is distinguished by the exact opposite - we cannot rely on person and no treaty is respected.
In these conditions, difficult to prepare Afghan security forces, accustomed to change leader from day to day depending on what suits them.
The political institutions, although based officially, will remain just window-dressing behind which will proliferate patriarchal ethnic relations.
It is particularly complex to balance the interests of various ethnic groups given the lack of clarity about the reports, which are further complicated by the Iranian and Pakistani influences.
Even the foundation of a "state quick to act", which is the basic purpose of the operation, does not seem to be very real.
The time horizon of the strategy Obama makes perplexed by his determination.
In the past eight years, the situation in Afghanistan has worsened and she is currently on the brink of chaos.
Only a heart purely romantic and outside reality can be confident that small soldiers sent in the tumult of the war for "prompt return home" will bring a real miracle.
From a political point of view, set a date for the withdrawal of troops is purely irresponsible because the Taliban will regard as the indirect admission of defeat.
The last NATO summit has shown that the will of Europeans to participate in military operations in Afghanistan is moving towards the negative.
European politicians know or do not want to explain to their constituents what security in Germany or Italy is linked to a war in the mountains of the Hindu Kush.
Another factor that can radically alter the situation is the evolution of events related to Iran.
If the situation continues to deteriorate and that the sanctions have no effect on the Iranians, the Americans will face of the very difficult issue of a resolution of the problem by the use of military force.
It will respond by example when, according to Obama, America will come to the victorious withdrawal of troops from Afghanistan.
Each solution of this type will, however, a dramatic reversal of the Afghan situation.
The only patch for Obama is the fact that there are three years until the presidential elections and therefore there is still enough time for that it is working on a new strategy, in case it would prove to be a flop.
The leaders of the bank Goldman Sachs will no longer receive bonuses in cash
Employees senior leaders of the US bank Goldman Sachs will not receive cash bonuses this year.
The company announced in response to strong criticism of its pay practices.
The group of 30 senior leaders will receive shares instead of money, they can not sell before five years.
The actions can be withdrawn to leaders in cases where they would take too many risks.
According to Reuters, Goldman Sachs arises as leader of the effort to link the rewards with long-term performance on Wall Street.
I suppose that Wall Street is well aware of the general sense that we must take, said the former investment banker Douglas Elliott of society JPMorgan
The concern is in the details, he added.
The bank Goldman Sachs has become the target of criticism after being set aside almost $17 billion in premiums on the first three quarters of this year.
For the current year, the total amount of premiums will probably 20 billion despite the measure announced today, according to Reuters.
With the arrival of the financial crisis, large bonuses in the banking sector have become a sensitive political issue in many countries.
Britain announced Wednesday that it had to assign a single fee of 50% bankers' bonuses exceeding 25,000 pounds.
France is preparing similar measures.
This year women won the Nobel Prize in all areas except the physical
These are five women, a record number, who received today in Stockholm from the hands of the King of Sweden Charles XVI Gustave the Nobel Prize in technical disciplines and literature.
In addition to the four scientists there was also the German writer of Romanian origin Herta Müller.
Two American biologists, Elizabeth Blackburn and Carol Greider received with their compatriot Jack Szostak the Nobel Prize for Medicine for their research in the field of chromosomes.
The prize for chemistry was awarded to the Israeli Ada Jonath with the Americans Venkatraman Ramakrishnan and Thomas Steitz for clarifying the structure and function of ribosomes
The last winner received the Nobel Prize in economics, the American Elinor Ostrom with his fellow countryman Oliver Williamson, for their analysis of economic governance.
The only technical discipline that has not been winner this year was the physical.
The prize was awarded today scientists Charles Kao for his research in the field of optical fibres and George Smith avecWillard Boyle for their invention of CCD chips, which are currently at the forefront of all digital cameras, fax or glasses astronomical.
Each winner received the diploma, the Nobel medal and certificate of acquisition of the financial reward.
It reached 10 million Swedish kronor in each category. (approximately 1.1 million euros)
If one of them has several winners, they will share the reward them.
The long-awaited Nobel Peace Prize has already been handed this afternoon in Oslo in Norway to US President Barack Obama.
In his speech, acknowledged the controversial nature of his reward since it is only at the beginning of his journey and that it is in addition to the head of a country engaged in two wars - in Iraq and Afghanistan.
In the discharge of its policy he added that in certain situations the war is essential to achieve peace, even if the price is high.
