It was not clear whether the comeback of the legendary hockey player will only one match.
I think that Fetissov is one of those who are able to strengthen the mental of other players, "said Nyemtchinov.
According to AP, in the case of his return on the ice, Fetissov becomes the Russian professional hockey player.
In NHL, the legendary attacking Gordie Howe played a season for Hartford and scored 15 goals and 26 assists.
The oldest of the famous quintet Fetissov, Kassatonov - Makarov, Larionov, Krutov is one of the best hockey players and among those with the most success.
Under the colours of the Soviet Union it has won twice the gold at the Olympic games, seven titles of world champion, he has triumphed at the Canada Cup and World Junior Championship.
In the second part of his career, he picked the tributes also in NHL where twice held the Stanley Cup.
